Before Development
* Create a project -> sudo ng new emi-calculator
* Select the stylesheet format
* Create the components header, section, footer using this syntax [sudo ng generate component xyz].
* Then add sudo ng add @angular/material also select the prebuilt theme.
* To install the slider -> Add the module (MatSliderModule) dependency in app.module.ts.
* To intall the pie chart -> sudo npm install jqwidgets-ng
* Add FormsModule in app.module.ts file

After Development
* Change the <base href="/"> to <base href="./">
* To take the build mkdir dist under your project folder.
* 